node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
1 lb strawberries sliced
1.5 cups sweetener
2 tbsp lemon juice
.
.
Instructions:
1. Add your strawberries to a sauce pan on medium heat and mix in the sugar. 
2. Stir until you bring the strawberries to a boil.
3. Once boiling add your lemon juice. 
4. Let boil for another 15 minutes / until jam reaches 220F stirring often so the jam doesn’t burn. 
5. Pour into a jar and let cool. 
.
.
#keto #ketorecipes #lowcarb #strawberries

node.text:
.
.
.
The Ellas Flats are such a bussin keto friendly option when you’re craving something light & crunchy 🙌 I highly reccomend you go order some! The link is in my bio 👍
.
.
Ingredients:
1/4 cup allulose 
2 TBSP butter
4-5 Ellas flats (link in bio)
1 tsp vanilla extract
1/8 tsp salt
.
.
Instructions:
1. Combine all ingredients except the flats in a non stick skillet over medium heat until the sweetener dissolves.
2. Add Flats and stir for 2-3 minutes.
3. Remove from stove and pour into a rimmed baking sheet / Pan lined with parchment paper. Spread peanuts evenly with a spoon. (Be careful it’s very hot)
4. Allow to cool for 1 hour. Break up into 4 servings and enjoy!
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketosnacks #ketotreats #ellasflats

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
1 can of chicken
1 large egg
1/2 cup shredded cheese
Seasonings of choice 
.
.
Instructions:
1. Mash your chicken up in a bowl and mix with all ingredients. 
2. Shape into nuggets and air fry on parchment paper at 400F for 8-10 minutes flipping halfway through.
3. Let cool & enjoy!
.
.
Notes: You can also bake at 400F for 20 mins flipping halfway.
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.title: Say “YES” if you would eat these ZERO CARB CHICKEN NUGGETS 😋🙌

Cheddar 
Egg
Butter
.

4. Pan fry in butter until golden brown on both sides. Enjoy!

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
2 lowcarb tortillas 
1 lb ground beef
1 cup marinara sauce
1 cup shredded mozarella
16 oz ricotta
1 cup grated parmesan
1 egg
1.5 tbsp oil
Seasonings of choice.
.
.
Instructions:
1. Cook ground beef, when finished, add marinara and switch heat to simmer until warm. Set aside.
2. Mix seasonings, ricotta, half of the Parmesan, and an egg in a bowl. Set aside.
3. In non stick or parchment lined baking dish add the meat sauce, tortilla, ricotta, meat sauce, mozzarella, parmesan & repeat .
4. Air fry at 400F for 10-12 mins. Slice into 4 squares. Enjoy!
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
1 lb strawberries sliced
1.5 cups sweetener
2 tbsp lemon juice
.
.
Instructions:
1. Add your strawberries to a sauce pan on medium heat and mix in the sugar. 
2. Stir until you bring the strawberries to a boil.
3. Once boiling add your lemon juice. 
4. Let boil for another 15 minutes / until jam reaches 220F stirring often so the jam doesn’t burn. 
5. Pour into a jar and let cool. 
.
.
#keto #ketorecipes #lowcarb #strawberries

Say “YES” if you would eat these breakfast cups! 😋🙌

Ingredients:
6 slices of ham
1/2 cup shredded cheese
6 large eggs
Seasonings of your preference 

Instructions:
1. Preheat oven to 360F 
2. Add your ham to a non stick muffin tin.
3. Sprinkle in your cheese, top with an egg and your seasonings.
4. Bake for 10-15 minutes.

#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.text:
Say “YES” if you would eat this chaffle bun pizza burger 🙌🍕🍔😋

To make it just mix 1 egg with 1/2 cup mozzarella and your favorite seasonings. Then add it to the waffle maker with pepperonis sandwiched between the mix and take it out when the light comes on. Repeat, add your burger & whatever else you want, and enjoy! 

#keto #lowcarb #ketodiet #lowcarbdiet #ketorecipes #chaffle

node.text:
Say “I forgive myself” if you had too many carbs over the weekend!! If you stayed strong leave a “💪” in the comments!!

I’ve been on both sides. My first year of keto I had a cheat day with allllll the worst carbs once a week. It was a terrible idea because I never got fat adapted, but I still lost a lot of weight so it was clearly better than eating junk food 24/7. Fast forward to now and I rarely cheat! Not only am I wayyyy healthier, I also have a better relationship with food. So if you’re still struggling, just keep going! It gets easier to turn down carbs over time! 🙏

The number one key to staying strong is to give yourself keto options for whatever you’re craving! There are so many recipes and products to replace carbs! The next most important thing is to be careful of your inner dialogue when faced with temptation. For example; Instead of saying “I love cookies” which makes it easy to justify a cookie, what if you said “I love the way cookies taste, but I hate the way they make me feel”. Wouldn’t that make it easier to stay strong when you’re hanging on by a thread?

When you stop to think about all of the baggage that comes with eating junk food, you can free yourself from the illusion that you somehow love it. Because unless you love being overweight and sick, you don’t actually love crappy food you just love the way it tastes.

If you ever need encouragement & positive vibes on your keto journey I’m always here for you 💕

#keto #lowcarb #ketodiet #lowcarbdiet #selflove

.
.
.
The Ellas Flats are such a bussin keto friendly option when you’re craving something light & crunchy 🙌 I highly reccomend you go order some! The link is in my bio 👍
.
.
Ingredients:
1/4 cup allulose 
2 TBSP butter
4-5 Ellas flats (link in bio)
1 tsp vanilla extract
1/8 tsp salt
.
.
Instructions:
1. Combine all ingredients except the flats in a non stick skillet over medium heat until the sweetener dissolves.
2. Add Flats and stir for 2-3 minutes.
3. Remove from stove and pour into a rimmed baking sheet / Pan lined with parchment paper. Spread peanuts evenly with a spoon. (Be careful it’s very hot)
4. Allow to cool for 1 hour. Break up into 4 servings and enjoy!
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketosnacks #ketotreats #ellasflats

node.text:
What is your favorite keto snack that you spend WAY too much money on?! 🤔 BTW.. if the meat sticks are high quality it’s more like $7 instead of $4 

It’s obviously cheaper to just make your own food, or buy healthier foods and spend less $ at the doctor later on, etc.. but impulse buying is hard to resist 😭

#keto #lowcarb #ketodiet #carnivore

node.text:
They poured the foundation!! 🙌

It doesn’t even feel real that less than 2 years ago I was living with my parents and now I’m a few months away from owning my own home!! I can’t wait to make all of the memories with my love @anafioreo and our two fur babies here ❤️

Thank you to everyone who has supported my content or bought my book! 💚🐢 None of this would be possible without you! 🙏 It’s a dream come true to make a living doing what fulfills my soul!
